const images = {
    userIcon: require('./svgs/userIcon.svg').default,
    logo: require('./imgs/logo2-transparent.png'),
    logoUI: require('./svgs/logoUI.svg').default,
    facebookIcon: require('./imgs/facebook.png'),
    instagramIcon: require('./imgs/instagram.png'),
    twitterIcon: require('./imgs/twitter.png'),
    linkedinIcon: require('./imgs/linkedin.png'),
    youtubeIcon: require('./imgs/youtube.png'),
    envelopeIcon: require('./imgs/envelope.png'),
    phoneCallIcon: require('./imgs/phone-call.png'),
    markerIcon: require('./imgs/marker.png'),
    userPng: require('./imgs/user-icon.png'),
    planePng: require('./imgs/plane-icon.png'),
    seatPng: require('./imgs/seat-icon.png'),
    caretDownPng: require('./imgs/caret-down.png'),
    tickPng: require('./imgs/tick-icon.png'),
    calendarIcon: require('./svgs/calendar.svg').default,
};

export default images;
